data.description: Custom built, beautiful 2 story home on 6.65 acres in a secluded country setting! Complete with an open floor plan, vaulted ceilings and beautiful wood floors. All stainless steel appliances included in this recently remodeled  eat in kitchen, that features a center island with a cooktop and plenty of cupboard space. You’ll love to entertain in the spacious living room, in front of the cozy wood burning fireplace. Also, on the first floor you will find a master bedroom with an ensuite bathroom, separate shower, garden tub, double sinks and walk in closet. On the second floor are 2 nice sized bedrooms which are connected by a recently remodeled jack and jill bathroom. There is a partially finished basement with so many possibilities to make it your own. Attached is a 3 car garage with plenty of space, and includes an entrance to the basement. A bonus 3 car detached pole barn/garage, with a loft, provides space for your workshop or to store your toys. Additionally, a whole house reverse osmosis water system and children’s playscape has been installed this summer. Major upgrades/updates to HAVC, sump pump, roof, septic, furnace, and electrical in 2020/21. Call for your private showing today.
